text.tspan: Death rate from road accidents for 15- to 49-year olds, 1990 to 2019
The annual number of deaths from road injuries per 100,000 individuals aged 15-49.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
Note: Deaths include those from drivers and passengers, motorcyclists, cyclists and pedestrians.
